\begin_layout Section
Conclusions and Future Work
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Future lensing surveys from EUCLID, WFIRST will uncover coarse data (not
 strong lensing features) but will derive cluster ensemble properties from
 weak shear (in fact detection will be driven by shear) -- these kinds of
 diagnostics can help us understand internal structure of clusters.
\end_layout

